casebody.data:
William G. Dominick, et al., respondents, v. C. C. Murphy, appellant. Decided February 2, 1885. Appeal from order referring the action to a referee to hear and determine the issues. Wingate & Cullen, for respondents. D. M. Helm, for appellant.

Before Sedgwick, Oh. J., and O’Gorman, J.

Opinion by O’Gorman, J. Order affirmed, with $10 costs.
